 -- Practise Tracker --

 Practise Tracker is my hobby project, designed as an alternative to proprietary time tracking apps that didn't have all of the features that I wanted.

 The main purpose of this app is it's namesake, to track the amount of time you spend practising. Additionally, it includes notes for each practise session, and goals that can span multiple sessions. Other features may be considered, however I am very much of the philosophy that applications should do one thing and they should do that one thing well, so I want to limit the amount of features.
